-- Control categories --
* Technical: OS, firewalls, AVs
* Managerial (org, policies): security policies, standard operating procedures
* Operational (people): security guards, posters, awareness, social engineering training
* Physical: fences, locks, CCTV

-- Control types --
* preventative: firewalls, locks, onboarding policies
* deterrent: threat of punishment, scary warning signs
* detective (to discover): system logs, login reports, motion detectors, property patrols
* corrective (after discovering): backup recovery, account lockout, calling cops, fire extinguisher
* compensating (temporary risk mitigation until better solution is avaiable): firewall blocks instead of patching the app
* directive (policies): file storage policies, "authorized personnel only" sign

